{"tid":1991180,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"餓賊兩劫旺角賓館    疫情影響生意僅劫得充電線","createTime":"2020-04-27T09:04:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-27T14:41:38.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d86d7ac8243e2901c84566ee9c54391cccbd3962","tid":1991180,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T09:04:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/i_SYRMo17jFa9iUsXIilNA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzQ3O2g9NjAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20200427a132914.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fi_SYRMo17jFa9iUsXIilNA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzQ3O2g9NjAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20200427a132914.jpg&h=de663601&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n女職員協助警方查。<br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】一名聲稱「無錢食飯」飢腸轆轆的中年男子，昨晚和今早先後行劫旺角長沙街同一間賓館，只劫得一條USB電話充電線。<br />\n<br />\n賓館位於長沙街2-16號，警方早上9時51分接報到場，在大廈地下截獲在場流連的賊人。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，賊人昨日闖入賓館聲稱行劫，但冷靜的女職員打開抽屜給賊人解釋，賓館在疫情下生意不景，賊人唯有搶走一條充電線後便離開。<br />\n<br />\n到今早，賊人折返現場，聲稱因肚餓「無錢食飯」而打劫，堅持不就範的女職員請相熟的房客幫忙退賊，並報警求助。"},{"pid":"b57872de5138db02ccf181c73ce1dc6bb2d6f6a5","tid":1991180,"uid":21842,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T09:12:56.000Z","msg":"2邊都好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a5606c3e24bec0c5f3bcd03870b41a4ef35a068","tid":1991180,"uid":5737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T09:22:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食過返尋味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以為人地次次都放佢走咁撚On9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2a631c0fc302f3f51dec67e78589b02869dd69c","tid":1991180,"uid":123848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T10:39:11.000Z","msg":"搶走一條充電線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解唔扮黑警呢"},{"pid":"83abe429fc93657af9e48d8d086d87e5e030d544","tid":1991180,"uid":236891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b57872de5138db02ccf181c73ce1dc6bb2d6f6a5","tid":1991180,"uid":21842,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T09:12:56.000Z","msg":"2邊都好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T14:33:47.000Z","msg":"好撚傷感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n被打劫都冇錢比人打"},{"pid":"1cc8ed4f6535486c2b99b07741d7701e7b0b10bc","tid":1991180,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T14:41:38.000Z","msg":"搶賓館點解唔搶鳳姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}